Package com.agorapulse.micronaut.aws.apigateway.ws.event

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Identity
    Simplified Identity of the WebSocket containing just the source IP address.
    RequestContext
    Request context sent with WebSocket event.
    WebSocketConnectionRequest
    Event which can be used as a parameter of Lambda functions which handles $connect or $disconnect route.
    WebSocketRequest
    Event which can be used as a parameter of Lambda functions which handles $default or user specified route.
    WebSocketResponse
    WebSocket response which always needs to be sent back from the function handling any of API Gateway WebSocket proxy events.
